title: alex arbuckle
content: I'm a software developer who lives in Kansas City, Missouri. I have a Bachelor of Science degree in **Computer Science**. Previously I've done contract work for a group of venture capitalists where I built **algorithms**, **visualization** and **interactivity** components for large sets of data.

As a developer, I consider myself a life-long learner, so I enjoy learning more about software development and deployment every opportunity I get. I'm a fan of both object-oriented and functional paradigms and I enjoy combining the skills I learn into projects that I display on my GitHub. *You can find more about them in **my projects**!*
